@startuml
' Diagram: F08 - Duyet hoac tu choi thanh toan goi app (Sequence)
' Status: WIP
' Baseline: branch master, HEAD b618c08
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/DuyetThanhToan/Index.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync(), OnGetPendingSnapshotAsync(), OnPostApproveAsync(), OnPostRejectAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/DuyetThanhToan/Index.cshtml: polling PendingSnapshot
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Models/YeuCauThanhToan.cs
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Models/DangKyApp.cs
' Note: Giu logic CMS PageModel hien tai; bo sung snapshot endpoint dung cho UI polling.
title F08 - Duyet hoac tu choi thanh toan goi app

actor Admin
participant "DuyetThanhToan.cshtml JS" as JS
participant "DuyetThanhToan IndexModel" as IndexModel
participant AppDbContext
database DB

Admin -> IndexModel: mo /DuyetThanhToan?tab=cho_duyet
IndexModel -> AppDbContext: query YeuCauThanhToans + Count(cho_duyet)
AppDbContext -> DB: SELECT yeu cau
DB --> AppDbContext: danh sach
IndexModel --> Admin: bang yeu cau

loop JS polling snapshot
  JS -> IndexModel: GET ?handler=PendingSnapshot
  IndexModel -> AppDbContext: Count(cho_duyet)\nOrderByDescending(NgayTao).First()
  AppDbContext -> DB: SELECT pending summary
  DB --> AppDbContext: count + latest
  IndexModel --> JS: JSON Count, LatestId, LatestTransferContent
end

alt admin duyet
  Admin -> IndexModel: POST Approve(yeuCauId)
  IndexModel -> AppDbContext: load YeuCauThanhToan + DangKyApp con han
  AppDbContext -> DB: SELECT current request/subscription
  DB --> AppDbContext: data
  IndexModel -> IndexModel: tinh mocBatDau + hetHan moi
  IndexModel -> AppDbContext: add DangKyApp\nupdate YeuCauThanhToan(da_duyet)
  AppDbContext -> DB: INSERT dangkyapp + UPDATE yeucauthanhtoan
  DB --> AppDbContext: saved
  IndexModel --> Admin: redirect tab da_duyet
else admin tu choi
  Admin -> IndexModel: POST Reject(yeuCauId, lyDo)
  IndexModel -> AppDbContext: load YeuCauThanhToan
  AppDbContext -> DB: SELECT request
  DB --> AppDbContext: request
  IndexModel -> AppDbContext: update TrangThai="tu_choi"\nNgayDuyet\nGhiChuAdmin
  AppDbContext -> DB: UPDATE yeucauthanhtoan
  DB --> AppDbContext: saved
  IndexModel --> Admin: redirect tab tu_choi
end
@enduml
